        <h3>JobTread — Best for small contractors who care about margins</h3>
        <p>JobTread at $99/month is the right choice for small contractors who've been burned by not knowing their actual job margin until after the fact. Its real-time job costing is genuinely excellent, and the platform is clean enough to start using productively within a day.</p>

        <div class="cta-box">
